OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FThe widow of a man who was killed at
OL,7,Fwork in Newry in 2022, says families
OL,8,Fare being held hostage because of
OL,9,Fdelays in the justice system due to
OL,10,Fthe ongoing barrister's strike.
OL,12,FIan McCollum was 52 when he was killed
OL,13,Fin a horrific incident at work.
OL,15,FOn Monday, 55-year-old Walter Manley,
OL,16,FLounder Crescent in Newry, who was due
OL,17,Fto go on trial, pleaded guilty to Mr.
OL,18,FMcCallum's manslaughter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FHis heartbroken family have had to
OL,7,Ffight to get this far because of the
OL,8,Fbarrister strike.
OL,10,FThe industrial action is part of a
OL,11,Flong-running dispute by criminal
OL,12,Fbarristers in Northern Ireland over
OL,13,Ffees for legal aid, which has seen
OL,14,Fcrown court cases involving those who
OL,15,Frequire legal aid effectively halted.
OL,17,FKathyrn McCollum, Ian's wife told UTV:
OL,18,F"They need to come to some compromise
OL,19,Fbecause so many people are just being
OL,20,Fheld hostage.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"I haven't even got my husband's death
OL,7,Fcertificate yet.
OL,9,F"That can't be issued by the coroner
OL,10,Funtil criminal proceedings are over.
OL,12,F"When I get that piece of paper in my
OL,13,Fhand, then the reality that he's
OL,14,Factually not ever coming back will set
OL,15,Fin, and that actually really scares
OL,16,Fme."
OL,18,FSentencing has been set for June, but
OL,19,FKathyrn fears they will face more
OL,20,Fdelays.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FShe continued: "His main love was
OL,7,Ffarming and his animals.
OL,9,F"If we hadn't used all of our resolve
OL,10,Fand strength and energy, Ian's trial
OL,11,Fwould just have been pushed back
OL,12,Findefinitely, and that would have been
OL,13,Fit."
OL,15,FThe couple's son Aaron said: "This
OL,16,Fwould have been lost into the ethers."
OL,18,FKathyrn added: "It's cruel to keep
OL,19,Fanyone living in a vacuum, unable to
OL,20,Fbreathe out."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FAaron continued: "Until this point,
OL,7,Fdad's been very much forgotten about.
OL,9,F"It's really frustrating and takes a
OL,10,Fgood emotional toll on you, having to,
OL,11,FI suppose, essentially jump through
OL,12,Fhoops to get to the point of where
OL,13,Fwe're at."
OL,15,FThe Department of Justice confirmed
OL,16,Fthere have been over 1,767 cases
OL,17,Fimpacted since the 5th of January 2026.
OL,19,FThis includes 313 trials, 1042
OL,20,Farraignments, and 412 plea and
OL,21,Fsentencing hearings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FThere is also an ongoing civil case
OL,7,Fthat has yet to be settled, adding to
OL,8,Fthe family's distress.
OL,10,FJustice Minister Naomi Long claimed on
OL,11,FTuesday that the strike action by
OL,12,Fcriminal barristers is damaging the
OL,13,Fjustice system and the credibility of
OL,14,Fthe criminal bar.
OL,16,FA derogation was granted to allow the
OL,17,Fcontinuation of some trials, including
OL,18,Fthat of the man accused of the murder
OL,19,Fof Natalie McNally in 2022, and the
OL,20,Ftrial of a man accused of Chloe
OL,21,FMitchell's murder in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FSpeaking during questions for the
OL,7,FJustice Minister at the Assembly, Ms
OL,8,FLong said she is expecting the outcome
OL,9,Fof a review into the issues raised.
OL,11,FDUP MLA Pam Cameron raised the case of
OL,12,FIan McCollum.
OL,14,FMs Cameron asked whether the strike
OL,15,Fwould be likely to have been resolved
OL,16,Fby the date of Walter Manley's
OL,17,F(pleaded guilty to Mr. McCallum's
OL,18,Fmanslaughter) sentencing on June 25th.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FMs Long said she has asked her
OL,7,Fofficials to assess the
OL,8,Frecommendations from the review and
OL,9,Ffor them to provide advice to her as a
OL,10,Fmatter of urgency.
OL,12,F"I hope that it will ultimately result
OL,13,Fin a return to service immediately.
OL,14,FHowever, as I said on the day when I
OL,15,Fmet with McCollum family, I believe
OL,16,Fthat the CBA ought to return to
OL,17,Fservice now," she told MLAs.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
