CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"You ought not to be in a position as
OL,7,Fa minister where you feel that you are
OL,8,Fnegotiating with a gun to your head,
OL,9,Fand essentially that is what's
OL,10,Fhappening.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
