PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"Because I am fearful too, of the
OL,7,Fattrition of victims and witnesses
OL,8,Fthrough these processes. I am
OL,9,Fconcerned about the impact on their
OL,10,Fmental health through the length of
OL,11,Fwait that they have, and I am
OL,12,Fconcerned about the impact in terms of
OL,13,Four wider justice system, where
OL,14,Fbacklogs build up and we do not have
OL,15,Fthe reserves in terms of the money to
OL,16,Fbe able to address those."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/18
