PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FShe went on: "It is doing damage to
OL,7,Fand justice system, and I would argue
OL,8,Fit is doing damage to the credibility
OL,9,Fof the criminal bar, and I would urge
OL,10,Fthem go back to work, come back to the
OL,11,Ftable and we will resolve these issues
OL,12,Fin a fair way, based on the evidence
OL,13,Fthat the accelerated review has
OL,14,Fpresented."
OL,16,FOpposition leader Matthew O'Toole
OL,17,Fqueried why the impasse remains
OL,18,Fongoing, putting it to the minister
OL,19,Fthat "this seems like a crisis that
OL,20,Fyou will not or cannot solve".
OL,26,@nD@NOUvD@KO]{D@FOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FMs Long responded: "The truth of the
OL,7,Fmatter is that there is nothing to
OL,8,Fstop the criminal bar coming back to
OL,9,Fwork at any time.
OL,11,F"It will not influence the outcome of
OL,12,Fthe accelerated review that they
OL,13,Fremain outside, it will not change the
OL,14,Foutcome of my deliberations on the
OL,15,Freport of that review.
OL,26,@nD@TOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
