OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"That arrives with me on April 24, and
OL,7,Fit is with my officials now for them
OL,8,Fto provide advice, which I anticipate
OL,9,Fgetting in the next few days, and I
OL,10,Fwill make quick decisions with regard
OL,11,Fto that in terms of a way forward.
OL,13,F"The only people who can control
OL,14,Fwhether or not they return to court
OL,15,Fare the criminal bar themselves, and I
OL,16,Fwould urge them to do so."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/18
