CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson for the
OL,7,FCriminal Bar Association said: "The
OL,8,FCriminal Bar Association has empathy
OL,9,Ffor families that are impacted by
OL,10,Fdelays across the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem, particularly in the most
OL,12,Fserious of cases before the Crown
OL,13,FCourt. The withdrawal of services was
OL,14,Ftaken as a last resort, and as a
OL,15,Fdirect result of years of review
OL,16,Finaction on the part of the Department
OL,17,Fof Justice. The CBA met with the
OL,18,FMcCollum family last week and listened
OL,19,Fto them on the impact of the delays in
OL,20,Ftheir case stretching to over four
OL,21,Fyears. We invited the McCollum family
OL,22,Fto meet us again if it would be of
OL,23,Fassistance.
OL,26,@oD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"Since the action was commenced at the
OL,7,Fstart of January 2026, the focus of
OL,8,Fcriminal barristers has been centred
OL,9,Fon working with the Department of
OL,10,FJustice to find sustainable solutions
OL,11,Fto the problems associated with the
OL,12,Fadministration of criminal Legal Aid
OL,13,Fand to enable all barristers to return
OL,14,Fto all Crown Court matters.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"To that end, we have been fully
OL,7,Fengaged with an ongoing Review of
OL,8,FCriminal Legal Aid, and more latterly
OL,9,Fan Accelerated Review of Criminal
OL,10,FLegal Aid. The findings of the
OL,11,FAccelerated Review were provided to
OL,12,Fthe Department of Justice on the 27th
OL,13,FApril and we await the Departmental
OL,14,Fresponse to the findings. The Minister
OL,15,Fconfirmed to the Assembly this
OL,16,Fafternoon (Tuesday) that her
OL,17,FDepartment has been in receipt of the
OL,18,Freview findings for some weeks now.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/18
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778746040
OL,3,CWidow says people 'held hostage' by
OL,4,Cbarrister strike delays
OL,6,F"It is the aim of the CBA that all
OL,7,Fbarristers make a return to Crown
OL,8,FCourt work as soon as possible and
OL,9,Fthat progress can be made on all
OL,10,Fcases. To that end the DoJ must act
OL,11,Fwith urgency and purpose on their
OL,12,Fresponse to the findings of the
OL,13,FAccelerated Review."
